<item chapterid="611761" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1962" articlename="恶魔总裁霸道宠：老婆，太惹火" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521907592" lastupdate="1521907592" chaptername="第315章判若两人" chapterorder="315" size="6287" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    “警察大哥，他醒过来了吗？”女孩子弱弱地问道，眼眶也有点红红的。

