<item chapterid="612273" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1962" articlename="恶魔总裁霸道宠：老婆，太惹火" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521907592" lastupdate="1521907592" chaptername="第824章丫头，慢点喝" chapterorder="827" size="6666" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    时间真是个魔鬼，无形中无意中就让他们之间果真有了一种陌生感。虽然爱还在心里，可是表面上他们却是显得那么陌生，谁也没有先开口――

