<item chapterid="612568" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1962" articlename="恶魔总裁霸道宠：老婆，太惹火" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521907592" lastupdate="1521907592" chaptername="第1119章魂不附体" chapterorder="1122" size="6680" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    这个男人，比他想象中的还要帅气英俊，还要英气逼人！

