<item chapterid="612570" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1962" articlename="恶魔总裁霸道宠：老婆，太惹火" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521907592" lastupdate="1521907592" chaptername="第1121章进入了热恋期" chapterorder="1124" size="6489" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    大年初六，丁华明乘坐下午一点的飞机，带着儿子飞回了北京。

